des:
Positivo Casa Inteligente products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

To enjoy, it will be necessary to connect Alexa to your Positivo products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Positivo Casa Inteligente" app in the app stores;
(2). Register your account or sign in with Facebook;
(3). You will need to have some Positivo Casa Inteligente devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Positivo Casa Inteligente app and name your devices accordingly to be used in "Positivo Casa Inteligente" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from the app stores;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Positivo Casa Inteligente" skill under "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Positivo Casa Inteligente", and you'll be navigated to the login page;
(9). Type your account and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the livingroom light"
“Alexa, turn off the livingroom light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"

“Alexa, turn off the smart Plug"
“Alexa, turn on the smart Plug"

If you have any problem when using this skill, you can contact us by sending an email to: relacionamento@positivo.com.br
